    <id-00001>
      <name type="string">Nutshell - Target Number Ladder</name>
      <text type="formattedtext"><p><b>Nutshell Target Number Ladder</b></p><p>4 Trivial</p><p>6 Routine</p><p>8 Standard</p><p>10 Tough</p><p>12 Hard</p><p>14 Extreme</p><p>Set the current TN with the host desktop widgets.</p></text>
    </id-00001>
    <id-00002>
      <name type="string">Nutshell - Strikes by Difference</name>
      <text type="formattedtext"><p><b>Strikes by Difference</b></p><p>Difference 0-1 = 1 Strike</p><p>Difference 2-4 = 2 Strikes</p><p>Difference 5-7 = 3 Strikes</p><p>Difference 8+ = 4 Strikes</p><p>Failure = 0 Strikes</p></text>
    </id-00002>
    <id-00003>
      <name type="string">Nutshell - Core Skill Rules</name>
      <text type="formattedtext"><p><b>Core Rolls</b></p><p>All skill and attack rolls are 2d6 + Skill.</p><p>Strikes Max = 4 + Endurance.</p><p>Strain Max = 4 + Power.</p><p>Skill values normally range from -2 to +3.</p><p>Total skill sum target is 5, with up to -3 total negatives.</p></text>
    </id-00003>
  </story>
